Error importing data: java.lang.RuntimeException: Caught NPE creating custom field with fieldName=Checklist key=com.gebsun.plugins.jira.issuechecklist__issue-checklist-field description=Checklist status, e.g. Completed. This field is deprecated, for more details please see: https://gebsun-confluence.atlassian.net/wiki/display/IC/Checklist+Completed+custom+field type.key=com.atlassian.plugins.atlassian-connect-plugin:com.gebsun.plugins.jira.issuechecklist__issue-checklist-field
